snippet.title: Amber Heard RECAST In Aquaman 2? - Emilia Clarke Playing Mera! - Rumor
snippet.description:
A lot of rumors are swirling that Emilia Clarke will be playing Mera in Aquaman 2, taking the place of Amber Heard. Let's talk about what it means if that were to happen! Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!! #AmberHeard #EmiliaClarke #Aquaman2
